Class CallableEventAtomicSink

  • java.lang.Object
    • fr.sorbonne_u.devs_simulation.models.events.EventSink
      • fr.sorbonne_u.devs_simulation.models.events.CallableEventAtomicSink
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class CallableEventAtomicSink
extends EventSink
    The class CallableEventAtomicSink implements an event sink descriptor that includes a reference to the sink model on which the methods of EventsExchangingI can be directly called

    Description

    When composing models and connecting them, static sink descriptors that are giving only the URIs of the models are progressively replaced by descriptors containing the references to the created models.

    Invariant

     invariant              true

    Created on : 2018-06-08

    Author:
    Jacques Malenfant
